title: Earth Harvest Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Organic, Take-out
description: A 100% vegan/vegetarian cafe serves vegan meals and treats. Drinks include organic fair trade coffees and teas with soy and almond milk options. Vegan cookies, cakes and desserts all made-in-house using organic flours. All soups are vegan and gluten free. Local and organic ingredients are used whenever possible.
